1209
01:24:17.774 --> 01:24:19.367
E quem era o analista dela?

1210
01:24:24.664 --> 01:24:26.741
Perguntei quem era o analista dela.

1211
01:24:35.632 --> 01:24:36.467
Eu era.

1212
01:24:39.247 --> 01:24:41.227
